1963年11月杨文明发动[[1963年南越政变|政变]]，吴廷琰和吴廷瑈被政变军[[阮文戎|阮文戎]]少校[[吴廷琰之死|乱枪打死于装甲车内]]。当时瑈夫人正和长女{{link-en|吴廷丽水|Ngô Đình Lệ Thủy}}在[[美国|美国]][[加州|加州]]。第二年瑈夫人尝试重返南越但被拒绝。她后来辗转[[罗马|罗马]]去了[[巴黎|巴黎]]。不久后的1967年4月，吴廷丽水在[[隆格瑞莫|隆格瑞莫]]死于车祸<ref>{{cite news|title=Crash Kills Mrs. Nhu's Daughter|publisher=[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]|date=1967-04-14|url=http://jfk.hood.edu/Collection/White%20Materials/White%20Assassination%20Clippings%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20II/Misc%20II-026.pdf|accessdate=2016-11-18|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305002550/http://jfk.hood.edu/Collection/White%20Materials/White%20Assassination%20Clippings%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20Folders/Miscellaneous%20II/Misc%20II-026.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，瑈夫人往[[法国|法国]][[蔚蓝海岸|蔚蓝海岸]]居住。

1986年7月24日，瑈夫人的父母（陈文章夫妇）双双被[[絞死|絞死]]在位于[[华盛顿|华盛顿]]的家中<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1986-07-26/news/mn-43_1_monk|title=Parents of Vietnam's Mme. Nhu Found Dead in Washington : Son Held in Murder of Diem Diplomats|publisher=Times Wire Services|date=1986-07-26|accessdate=2016-11-18|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305074038/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-07-26/news/mn-43_1_monk|dead-url=no}}</ref>，瑈夫人之弟陈文谦因此被指认为嫌疑人，但证据不足。<ref>[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]] [http://articles.latimes.com/1987-11-05/news/vw-18789_1_vietnamese-family A Journey From Glory to the Grave - Prominent Vietnamese Family's Saga Began in Palace, May End in Court in the Wake of a Double Death] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1987-11-05/news/vw-18789_1_vietnamese-family |date=20110101173327 }} November 05, 1987</ref>

2011年4月24日因長期患病，病逝於[[意大利|意大利]][[羅馬|羅馬]]。

